name: BNC Turbine Air Cleaner
description:
Slotted air cleaner with hidden hadware gives a stealth look to any stock or custom. Machined from 6061-T6 billet aluminum with a chrome plated cover. Includes a K&N high flow element and stainless steel mounting hardware. Comes with a head breather support bracket that allows the motor to breathe through the air cleaner for a clean appearance. Bolts directly to S&S super E,G, stock CV carburetors and delphi EFI including 08 and later touring models. Bolts to a Mikuni using a standard adapter.  

Specify year and model when ordering.

100% MADE IN USA!
